  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, the cricket gloves trial sounds exciting! I’m curious — did the players give good feedback?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Most say they’re comfortable, but some want better grip. I’m working on that. By the way, did you see the new Shah Rukh movie? It’s a hit!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Great! Working on grip is part of the process. As for the movie, I haven’t seen it yet — are you planning to watch it?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I watched it last weekend. The acting is top-notch, but the story is a bit predictable. Still, it's worth a watch if you like SRK. I'm thinking of watching it again with friends this Friday."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds fun! Watching with friends always makes it better. What time do you usually watch movies with them?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Mostly evenings, around 7 or 8. We grab some popcorn and chill. Oh, and we sometimes watch Bollywood songs first—*so* much fun!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Evenings are perfect for movies and fun. You enjoy Bollywood songs too — any favorite ones to sing along?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, \"Tum Hi Ho\" from \"Aashiqui 2\" is a favorite. We all sing it loudly, even if off-key! But hey, it's the vibe that counts. I should go now — need to prep for a meeting. Talk later!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You go — meetings first! \"Tum Hi Ho\" is a great pick. Let me know how your meeting goes. Take care!"
    }
  ],
